cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an invalid format '999.999.999.999' will cause network connectivity failures and AMF association errors.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_ConfigurationIndex to a negative value (-1) will cause RACH configuration validation errors as the index must be non-negative.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_ConfigurationIndex 設定為負值 (-1) 會導致 RACH 配置驗證錯誤，因為索引必須為非負數。
